Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located along the California coast!

Name: Bruce's Beach
Description: A scenic park with stunning and breathtaking views of the ocean!

Name: Mount Tamalpais
Description: Also known as Mount Tam, is the highest point in Marin County with incredible views of the ocean and the bay from above the clouds!

Name: Rio Celeste Waterfall
Description: Surrounded by a tropical forest, the waterfall is submerged in nature flowing through the Tenorio Volcano National Park!

Name: Jackson Hole
Description: A huge mountain with diverse terrain and great quality snow for snowboarding!

Name: Ithaki Beach
Description: Crystal clear beach only accessible by boat with vibrant, warm blue water, sea shells, and cliffs to jump off of!
